(128556, 'Trapped by King Kobra!', 16251, 'Kid Colt helps finds out that Sam Hawk plans to attack a dangerous gang and he brings them down himself to save him.', NULL, 'This story is divided into two parts: chapter one—"Into the Valley of Doom!" (7 pp) and part two—"The Hunter and the Hunted!" (6 pp). Sam Hawk last appears in Gunsmoke Western (Marvel 1955 series) #60 (September 1960) and next appears in issue #101 (November 1961).', 19),
